    '株式会社エアロラボインターナショナルは、企業理念を実現するためには、お客様の信頼を得ることを第一と考え、ここに「情報セキュリティ基本方針」を定め、下記事項を常に念頭に置き、経営陣を含め全従業員に周知徹底し、この方針に従い適切な情報資産の保護に努めてまいります。': 'Aerolab International Inc. considers earning the trust of our customers to be the foundation for fulfilling our corporate philosophy. We hereby establish this "Information Security Policy," keep the following items in mind at all times, ensure that all employees including management are fully informed, and strive to protect our information assets appropriately in accordance with this policy.',
